item.description:
"Date Me I'm Jewish" invites you to an evening of speed dating and dinner for Jewish singles 40 -65 at the Imperial China Restaurant in Framingham, MA on Sunday, June 28th from 5:30 - 9 PM. The cost is only $39 per person which includes: speed dating, buffet dinner, taxes & tip. Cash bar is available. Free parking.

You can expect to have up to 20 dates in one evening.

Our speed dating events have always sold out fast.
Don't be left out! Reserve your space today!
Advance registration before 6/24 is required.

For information and registration, click http://singles.meetup...
OR call Barry at 508-333-1466 or Stan at 508-572-9049.
item.name: Speed Dating with Date Me I'm Jewish
